			<h2>Welcome to COMPUTERBILD Safer surfing 2010.07</h2>
			<ul>
				<li><p>Double click the symbol "Network connection" on the desktop if you want to connect to the internet.
				This starts the program to configure WLAN and LAN connections. Other types of connection 
				do not work yet.</p></li>
				<li><p>The symbol "Search for updates" in the menubar allows you to update this system. This function is 
				only available if booted with the option "Full startup"!</p></li>
				<li><p>If you want to listen to music or watch videos, you have to turn on sound by 
				clicking on the loudspeaker symbol on the right side of the menu bar.</p></li>
			</ul>
			<p>
